               <p>JOHN PIPE. I lost this money on the 2nd of September, from my shop, in <placeName id="t18300916-356-crimeloc1836">King-street, St. Giles'</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300916-356-crimeloc1836" type="placeName" value="King-street, St. Giles'"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18300916-356-crimeloc1836" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-356-off1834 t18300916-356-crimeloc1836"></join>. I saw the prisoner take it from the till about nine o'clock at night; I went into the shop before he put the money into his pocket - I went in; he took out 3 1/2d., and said that was all he had taken - I kept him, I dare say, an hour, when the officer came and took him; I had searched him before the officer came, and found 1s. 1d. on him - he had taken the sovereign before from a parcel which I sent him out with; he was in my employ.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-356-person2890">
